data.description: Approaching this property you will be instantly impressed with the unique design of the home. Cedar shake siding, circular drive and tasteful landscape. In the rear you will presently surprised with the patios, pergola and fenced yard and roses galore in season. Incredible opportunity to own this well-designed home with an open concept and natural lighting throughout. Lg tiled entry foyer with beautiful staircase that will surely catch the eye. Generously sized family room open to dining filled with amazing windows & high ceilings, double sided gas log fireplace & hardwood floors. Spacious primary bed rm w/ 2 walk-in closets, has ensuite w/ spa tub & walk-in shower. Stove, dishwasher, microwave, floors refinished, updated lighting fixtures in 22.
